_sText:
This is a mashup map that combines Smee Tower with Ski Mountain, including noteworthy features from various community edits of each map.

The maps used are as follows:
  • mg_ski_mountain_fix_v2 by Tomgreen
  • mg_ski_mountain_resort_fix by ProfessorOak
  • mg_smee_tower_fix2 by Mathijs
  • mg_smee_tower_defuse by Crunchy
  • mg_smee_tower_lite_v2_1 by Biggles

The tower is placed at the bottom of the large ski ramp, replacing the resort that was put there. Players may either spawn near the tower or at the top of the ramp. Every secret from each map was implemented in some form.
